message.text:
𝐀𝐘𝐈-𝐧𝐜𝐫𝐞𝐝𝐢𝐛𝐥𝐞 𝐝𝐚𝐲 𝐟𝐨𝐫 𝐒𝐢𝐭𝐭𝐢𝐞. 💖💐

Today, we celebrate not just your special day, but also the laughter, and kindness that you bring to everyone around you. 𝐀𝐬 𝐓𝐡𝐞 𝐕𝐢𝐜𝐞 𝐏𝐫𝐞𝐬𝐢𝐝𝐞𝐧𝐭 𝐨𝐟 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐒𝐭𝐫𝐚𝐢𝐠𝐡𝐭 𝐏𝐞𝐨𝐩𝐥𝐞, you’ve shown us how fun, genuine, and warm-hearted you truly are. 💖

Your presence has always been such a gift, and we’re grateful for all the memories we’ve shared with you.

Happiest birthday once again, Sittie—you deserve all the love and joy this world has to offer! 🎉

Pubmat by: Miguelito Lalu
Caption by: Chelsea Ann Menor

#Ayi’sDay
#FROMLGBTQRFAM

message.text:
𝐀𝐘𝐈-𝐧𝐜𝐫𝐞𝐝𝐢𝐛𝐥𝐞 𝐝𝐚𝐲 𝐟𝐨𝐫 𝐒𝐢𝐭𝐭𝐢𝐞. 💖💐

Today, we celebrate not just your special day, but also the laughter, and kindness that you bring to everyone around you. 𝐀𝐬 𝐓𝐡𝐞 𝐕𝐢𝐜𝐞 𝐏𝐫𝐞𝐬𝐢𝐝𝐞𝐧𝐭 𝐨𝐟 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐒𝐭𝐫𝐚𝐢𝐠𝐡𝐭 𝐏𝐞𝐨𝐩𝐥𝐞, you’ve shown us how fun, genuine, and warm-hearted you truly are. 💖

Your presence has always been such a gift, and we’re grateful for all the memories we’ve shared with you.

Happiest birthday once again, Sittie—you deserve all the love and joy this world has to offer! 🎉

Pubmat by: Miguelito Lalu
Caption by: Chelsea Ann Menor

Hi, I’m Lyn from Las Ve- AY! Wala po bang take 2, direk 😅?

Hey Marketistas 👋! 

⭐️ We’re the Talents Management Department—the home of all the talented marketistas. ⭐️

🎸 Are you a musician? 
💃 Dancer? 
🤸‍♂️ Athlete? 
👤 Or maybe a leader with a passion for people management?

If so, this opportunity may be for you 🫵🏼!

🗯 Here’s what we’ve got:

🎸 JMA Musikeros
We’ll give you the stage to share your incredible tunes!

💃 JMA Dance Squad
We have the platforms where you can pop it, lock it, and drop it!

🤸‍♀️ JMA Athletes
We’ve got your backs as you aim for the GOLD!

Sports we cover:
Basketball 
Volleyball
Badminton
Table Tennis
Chess
E-games (Valorant, ML)

👩‍🏫 Talents Management STP
Sharpen your talent management skills!

You could be our one in a million, so come be our star ⭐️!

No need to email us.. Just answer these forms..

STP Applications: https://bit.ly/2025-2026STP

SCM Applications: https://bit.ly/2025-2026SCM

Membership Applications: https://bit.ly/FEUJMAMEMBERS

Talents Membership: https://bit.ly/FEUJMATALENTS

#LakbayPiyu2025
#SOARsogonWithFEUJMA
#30YearsOneFEUJMA
#AboveAndBeyondFEUJMA

Hi, I’m Lyn from Las Ve- AY! Wala po bang take 2, direk 😅?

Hey Marketistas 👋! 

⭐️ We’re the Talents Management Department—the home of all the talented marketistas. ⭐️

🎸 Are you a musician? 
💃 Dancer? 
🤸‍♂️ Athlete? 
👤 Or maybe a leader with a passion for people management?

If so, this opportunity may be for you 🫵🏼!

🗯 Here’s what we’ve got:

🎸 JMA Musikeros
We’ll give you the stage to share your incredible tunes!

💃 JMA Dance Squad
We have the platforms where you can pop it, lock it, and drop it!

🤸‍♀️ JMA Athletes
We’ve got your backs as you aim for the GOLD!

Sports we cover:
Basketball 
Volleyball
Badminton
Table Tennis
Chess
E-games (Valorant, ML)

👩‍🏫 Talents Management STP
Sharpen your talent management skills!

You could be our one in a million, so come be our star ⭐️!

No need to email us.. Just answer these forms..

STP Applications: https://bit.ly/2025-2026STP

SCM Applications: https://bit.ly/2025-2026SCM

Membership Applications: https://bit.ly/FEUJMAMEMBERS

Talents Membership: https://bit.ly/FEUJMATALENTS

#LakbayPiyu2025
#SOARsogonWithFEUJMA
#30YearsOneFEUJMA
#AboveAndBeyondFEUJMA

Edited by Dana Cordero
Caption by Dana Cordero

message.text:
The spirit of green and gold came alive to  light up UAAP Season 88 with TAMRally 2025.

With drums, horns, flags, cheers echoing, the university kicked off its UAAP Season 88 journey in high-energy passion. The FEU Drum and Bugle Corps led the  parade, whose rhythms had the crowd on their feet from the very first beat. The Green and gold pride was in full swing, setting the tone for a season that’s bound to be thrilling, competitive, and unforgettable. With this kind of energy, FEU is clearly ready to chase the Gold in UAAP Season 88!

#FEUDBC 
#GoldIsTheGoal
#PlantingTheFEUture

message.text:
The spirit of green and gold came alive to  light up UAAP Season 88 with TAMRally 2025.

With drums, horns, flags, cheers echoing, the university kicked off its UAAP Season 88 journey in high-energy passion. The FEU Drum and Bugle Corps led the  parade, whose rhythms had the crowd on their feet from the very first beat. The Green and gold pride was in full swing, setting the tone for a season that’s bound to be thrilling, competitive, and unforgettable. With this kind of energy, FEU is clearly ready to chase the Gold in UAAP Season 88!

#FEUDBC 
#GoldIsTheGoal
#PlantingTheFEUture

message.text:
The spirit of green and gold came alive to  light up UAAP Season 88 with TAMRally 2025.

With drums, horns, flags, cheers echoing, the university kicked off its UAAP Season 88 journey in high-energy passion. The FEU Drum and Bugle Corps led the  parade, whose rhythms had the crowd on their feet from the very first beat. The Green and gold pride was in full swing, setting the tone for a season that’s bound to be thrilling, competitive, and unforgettable. With this kind of energy, FEU is clearly ready to chase the Gold in UAAP Season 88!

#FEUDBC 
#GoldIsTheGoal
#PlantingTheFEUture

message.text:
The spirit of green and gold came alive to  light up UAAP Season 88 with TAMRally 2025.

With drums, horns, flags, cheers echoing, the university kicked off its UAAP Season 88 journey in high-energy passion. The FEU Drum and Bugle Corps led the  parade, whose rhythms had the crowd on their feet from the very first beat. The Green and gold pride was in full swing, setting the tone for a season that’s bound to be thrilling, competitive, and unforgettable. With this kind of energy, FEU is clearly ready to chase the Gold in UAAP Season 88!

#FEUDBC 
#GoldIsTheGoal
#PlantingTheFEUture

message.text:
The spirit of green and gold came alive to  light up UAAP Season 88 with TAMRally 2025.

With drums, horns, flags, cheers echoing, the university kicked off its UAAP Season 88 journey in high-energy passion. The FEU Drum and Bugle Corps led the  parade, whose rhythms had the crowd on their feet from the very first beat. The Green and gold pride was in full swing, setting the tone for a season that’s bound to be thrilling, competitive, and unforgettable. With this kind of energy, FEU is clearly ready to chase the Gold in UAAP Season 88!

#FEUDBC 
#GoldIsTheGoal
#PlantingTheFEUture
